# Internal coordination / agent-state files (DEC-007) — kept private
# These are session scratchpads with agent back-and-forth, preliminary decisions,
# and development-process noise. Public users should read CLAUDE.md,
# docs/architecture.md, and docs/design/* instead.
HANDOFF.md
TODOS.md
MEMORY.md
DECISIONS.md
CHANGELOG-DEV.md

