# glyphling-specific: GIF export outputs (TODO-008)
# Users running `glyphling export` locally shouldn't commit captures.
# Intentional repo assets (demos, README GIFs) go under docs/assets/ and must be added explicitly.
*.gif
*.tape
!docs/assets/**/*.gif
!docs/assets/**/*.tape
!docs/demos/tapes/*.tape

# Package tarballs from local `npm pack` / release dry-runs
*.tgz
*.tar.gz
glyphling-*.tgz

# Python (in case any tooling ever pulls a venv into the tree)
